1
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:11,000
Mami!

2
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:17,000
Oči!

3
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Binka!

4
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,000
Brina!

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:30,352
No, zato bom pa napisala pismo vili straniščki.

6
00:00:30,352 --> 00:00:34,056
No, le tako dosežeš, da se kaj spremeni.

7
00:00:34,056 --> 00:00:35,630
Oranžna luč, oči.

8
00:00:35,630 --> 00:00:36,000
Ops!

9
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:36,444
Oči!

10
00:00:36,444 --> 00:00:39,777
Zapeljal si skozi oranžno luč!

11
00:00:39,777 --> 00:00:41,444
Ja, ja, pa res.

12
00:00:41,444 --> 00:00:43,000
Je nisi videl?

13
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Ja, sem jo.

14
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:43,000
A pri oranžni zmanjšaš hitrost in ustaviš.

15
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Zakaj nisi upočasnil in ustavil?

16
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Ah, no, poseben primer je bil.

